		"description": "Complete workflow for ApiForge Headless CMS.\n\n**Setup Order:**\n1. Run '01 Auth'\n2. Run '02 Media' (Optional)\n3. Run '03 Content Types' (Define Schema)\n4. Run '04 Permissions' (Grant Access)\n5. Run '05 Content Entries' (CRUD)",
